<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sun-n">sun <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sʌn/    美 /sʌn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-the">1.★ <strong>[常与the连用] 太阳：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>The sun rises / sets</strong>. 
太阳升起/落下。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We talked about <strong>everything under the sun</strong>. 
天南地北我们无所不谈。</p></div>

<p>注: sun与某一特定形容词连用时，用不定冠词。   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a burning sun 
炎热的太阳</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 阳光：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>in the sun</strong> 
在阳光下</p></div></div>